title: Sochi 2014 Olympic Winter Games - Opening Ceremony (minus athlet
description:
Recorded from Australian free-to-air digital broadcast on channel One.
8 February 2014

Has a few minor glitches from digital TV reception, but pretty smooth overall.

This version is ABRIDGED meaning that the long, boring bits have been cut out.  The two removed sections are the athlete entrances (except for Greece and Australia) and the two speeches.  Everything else remains.

I will also upload a full unabridged version also.
